This paper involves computer vision techniques for facial expression recognition, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the study involves human cognition and perception, which could also be classified under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of saliency maps also involves machine learning and data analysis, which could be classified under multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
